Package: moppr
Title: Posterior inference using a mixture of partial posteriors
Version: 0.4.2
Date: 2022-07-03
Authors@R: person("Marc", "Box", email = "marc.box@protonmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Implementation of the MoPP algorithm with examples. MoPP 
    facilitates sample-based Bayesian inference when data are partitioned and 
    parts distributed across nodes of a cluster or held by different parties.
License: GPL (>=3)
